resources.string: Set the user data for whom you want to calculate the body fat rate
Male is "men" and the female is "woman"
Unit is cm. The range is 40~240cm
Only supports children above 10 years old and adults under 80 years old. For those under 10 years old, only weight and BMI data are valid

When "First Time" is selected, each device will only return once for a single scan. When "Every Time" is selected, a single scan of each device may be called back multiple times, but the signal strength will be different

kg default value 
lb pounds, all scales can support this unit 
 kg, if the scale end does not support, it will display kg
st stone, if the scale end does not support will display lb
Your age is less than 10 years old, you can not get accurate measurement data when testing
After setting the time, if no Bluetooth device is scanned within the specified time, the error message will be returned

Scan duration unit is ms, the default is 0, that is, the scan is always performed, unless the APP calls stopBleDeviceDiscovery. If it is not 0, the minimum value is 3000ms, it will delay the time after the duration ms, automatically Stop scanning.
Athlete mode for regular sports users
